This is tic-tac-toe game
it's a two player game where players take turn placing X's and 0's on a 3X3 board.
The game utilises the conditional statements and a nested loop

The player selects a random between 1 and 9.
The number is checked if, it's in place. if not the number is printed on the boord as letter X or O.

To win the game, one player's letter must match either horizontally, diagonally or vertically.
After winning the game, a message is displayed on the dashboard with letter the assigned to the player.

Also, players can tie. that is if the board has accumulated all the letters from both sides.

The computer is being used, as a second player to make the game interactive.

welcome. Let's play and good luck.
